"Pasa la propiedad JDBC <literal>propertyName</literal> a "
"<literal>DriverManager.getConnection()</literal>."

#: index.docbook:700
msgid ""
"<property>hibernate.jndi.</property><emphasis>&lt;propertyName&gt;</emphasis>"
